# BCL SCORING — Perspektif, Indikator, BIM Use & ISO 19650 Mapping

## Bobot Organisasi (FIXED)

| Perspektif | Bobot |
|------------|--------|
| P1 Governance & Strategy | 15% |
| P2 Process & Workflow | 30% |
| P3 Information & Model Quality | 20% |
| P4 People & Capability | 15% |
| P5 Value, Impact & Risk Reduction | 20% |
| **Total** | **100%** |

Bobot berlaku untuk seluruh proyek.

---

# P1 — Governance & Strategy (15%)

Fokus: Tata kelola dan kontrol implementasi BIM.

| Indikator | BIM Use Terkait | ISO 19650 Mapping |
|------------|-----------------|------------------|
| EIR / BEP tersedia & disetujui | All BIM Use | ISO 19650-2 §5 Information Requirements |
| Struktur CDE sesuai standar | All | ISO 19650-1 & 2 — CDE Principles |
| Role BIM ditetapkan formal | All | ISO 19650-2 — Information Management Roles |
| Rencana BIM Use terdokumentasi | Coordination / 4D / 5D | ISO 19650-2 — Planning Phase |
| Review koordinasi terjadwal | Clash / Coordination | ISO 19650-2 — Information Delivery Planning |
| KPI BIM terdefinisi | Value / Risk | ISO 19650-1 — Organizational Level |
| Risiko BIM di risk register | Risk Reduction | ISO 19650 — Risk & Information Control |
| Approval workflow digital berjalan | Publishing / Delivery | ISO 19650 — Information Approval Status |

---

# P2 — Process & Workflow (30%)

Fokus: Penggunaan nyata BIM dalam proses proyek.

| Indikator | BIM Use Terkait | ISO 19650 Mapping |
|------------|-----------------|------------------|
| Model koordinasi lintas disiplin | Design Coordination | ISO 19650-2 §5 Delivery |
| Clash detection berkala | Clash Detection | ISO 19650 — Coordination Process |
| Issue tracking aktif | BCF / Issue Mgmt | ISO 19650 — Information Tracking |
| Model untuk shopdrawing | Detailed Design | ISO 19650 — Information Production |
| Model untuk quantity take-off | 5D | ISO 19650 — Use of Information |
| Model untuk 4D planning | 4D | ISO 19650 — Project Delivery |
| Update model sesuai progres | Progress Update | ISO 19650 — Information Revision |
| RFI terkait model terdokumentasi | Coordination | ISO 19650 — Information Exchange |
| Workflow revisi terdokumentasi | All | ISO 19650 — Change Control |
| Sinkronisasi model–drawing | Model-Based Delivery | ISO 19650 — Consistency Principle |

---

# P3 — Information & Model Quality (20%)

Fokus: Kualitas dan integritas informasi.

| Indikator | BIM Use Terkait | ISO 19650 Mapping |
|------------|-----------------|------------------|
| Naming convention konsisten | All | ISO 19650-1 — Naming Rules |
| Level of Information Need terpenuhi | All | ISO 19650-1 §11 |
| Parameter utama konsisten | 5D / Asset Data | ISO 19650 — Information Quality |
| Version control berjalan | All | ISO 19650 — Revision Control |
| Model audit internal | Coordination | ISO 19650 — Validation |
| Tidak ada duplikasi file aktif | All | ISO 19650 — Single Source of Truth |
| Status model jelas (WIP/Shared/Published) | All | ISO 19650 — CDE Workflow |
| Clash residual terkendali | Clash Detection | ISO 19650 — Validation & Coordination |

---

# P4 — People & Capability (15%)

Fokus: Kapabilitas & keberlanjutan kompetensi.

| Indikator | BIM Use Terkait | ISO 19650 Mapping |
|------------|-----------------|------------------|
| Kompetensi sesuai role | All | ISO 19650 — Organizational Capability |
| Pelatihan BIM terdokumentasi | All | ISO 19650 — Resource Planning |
| Knowledge sharing dilakukan | All | ISO 19650 — Continuous Improvement |
| SOP BIM tersedia | All | ISO 19650 — Information Management Procedure |
| Evaluasi performa BIM dilakukan | All | ISO 19650 — Performance Review |
| SLA respons issue BIM | Coordination | ISO 19650 — Collaboration Control |

---

# P5 — Value, Impact & Risk Reduction (20%)

Fokus: Dampak nyata terhadap proyek.

| Indikator | BIM Use Terkait | ISO 19650 Mapping |
|------------|-----------------|------------------|
| Pengurangan rework terukur | Coordination | ISO 19650 — Risk Mitigation |
| Pengurangan clash konstruksi | Clash Detection | ISO 19650 — Validation |
| Akurasi quantity meningkat | 5D | ISO 19650 — Information Use |
| Efisiensi waktu koordinasi | Coordination | ISO 19650 — Collaboration |
| Transparansi progres meningkat | 4D | ISO 19650 — Delivery Monitoring |
| As-built berbasis model | Asset Information | ISO 19650-3 |
| Pelaporan manajemen berbasis model | Reporting | ISO 19650 — Information Use |
| BIM dipakai dalam keputusan | Strategic Use | ISO 19650 — Organizational Integration |

---

# Prinsip Penting

- Mapping ISO 19650 bersifat alignment, bukan klaim compliance otomatis.
- Skor mencerminkan implementasi nyata, bukan hanya dokumen tersedia.
- Indikator boleh diaktifkan/dinonaktifkan sesuai BIM Use proyek.
- Bobot perspektif tetap dan tidak berubah.

---

# Output Sistem

- BIM Score (0–100)
- Confidence Metric (0–1 atau %)
- Breakdown per Perspektif
- Breakdown per Indikator
- Audit trail & Evidence link
